snippet.title: EVE Online: Ascension Feature Tour
snippet.description:
EVE Online: Ascension Feature Tour
The November 15th 2016 Ascension expansion is a free addition to EVE that brings a whole host of new features and some of the biggest changes ever to New Eden. It introduces Clone States, allowing you to play for free as an Alpha clone for as long as you want. The improved New Player Experience makes it easier than ever for your or your friends to learn how to play. We have also added three impressive engineering complexes, new ships, command bursts, a fitting simulator, new explosion effects, and much more.

Visit http://updates.eveonline.com/ for the latest updates, expansions, and player gatherings 

Subscribe to our channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCwF3VyalTHzL0L-GDlwtbRw
Join us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/eveonline
